# DUP Workout Tracker

A Progressive Web App for tracking Daily Undulating Periodization (DUP) workouts with RPE-based training.

## Features

- ğŸ“Š Track workouts with sets, reps, and RPE
- ğŸ“ˆ Progress tracking for Big 3 lifts (Squat, Bench, Deadlift)
- âœï¸ Fully customizable exercises and programs
- ğŸ’¾ All data saved locally (works offline)
- ğŸ“± Install as standalone app on mobile devices
- ğŸ”„ Automatic DUP session rotation (Strength/Hypertrophy/Power)

